;                      pp. 343-355, (2008).
;               6)  Roux, A., O. Le Contel, C. Coillot, A. Bouabdellah, B. de la Porte,
;                      D. Alison, S. Ruocco, and M.C. Vassal "The Search Coil
;                      Magnetometer for THEMIS," Space Sci. Rev. 141,
